=======================================================
Project1 - Client Server using Socket Programming
	   Author  - 	Atharva Ghaisas

=======================================================


USAGE:

Server
==============================

1.run make command to compile both client and server then run exe named SERVER on one machine.
2. command -
  ./SERVER

Client
==============================
1.run make command to compile both client and server then run exe named SERVER on one machine.
2. command -
   1.	./CLIENT <IP_address_of_machine_running_server_program>	(use this if client and server both are running on the different machines in the same network).

   2.	./CLIENT   (Use this if client and server are both running on the same machine).			

3.send exit in message to client to stop the communication.
 e.g. To Client : exit

